HW 4:- SQL

1.	Explain the difference between Left & Right join With sample queries?
Left join queries show  all the columns & rows from the left side & right side
Syntax: select * from (table name) Left Join (Table name) on (left table column name= right table column name)
Right join queries show all the columns & rows from the right side table


2.	Find the name of the person who has max salary in a given table?
SELECT MAX (column Name) FROM (table name)


3.	Explain the difference between group by & order by clause


4.	Explain the difference between where & having



5.	Give the syntax of Update query
UPDATE (COLUMN NAME)
SET (COLUMN NAME=Value)
WHERE (COLUMN NAME =Value)





